examples.en: Quit nagging! I already said I'm not going.
Lee had a nagging pain in her back.
She keeps nagging me about my weight.
If she keeps on nagging at her husband like that, he'll leave her.
For crying out loud, stop nagging!
I had a nagging doubt in the back of my mind.
Mom's always nagging me about my hair.
My parents are always nagging me to clean my room.
'Will you leave off nagging?' he snarled.
There was still a nagging doubt in the back of her mind.
There was still one little nagging doubt at the back of his mind.
I had a nagging presage that the results of my medical tests would not be good.
